quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,Al-Qariah (The great Calamity)
  101,2,What is the great Calamity
  101,3,And what made you realise what is the great Calamity
  101,4,The Day mankind becomes like moths scattered about
  101,5,"And the mountains become like wool, fully carded"
  101,6,"Then as for that: whose weights (of good deeds) became heavy —"
  101,7,so he will be in happy life in complete agreement (of the Will of God)
  101,8,"And as for that: whose weights (of good deeds) became light (and insignificant)"
  101,9,then his parent place will be Hawiyah
  101,10,"And what made you realise what it is, that one"
  101,11,(It is the) Fire extremely hot and fiercely blazing